race.description: Astute Finance Call Bec Or Brent Handicap (C1)
race.comment: ALL ADORE (7) nice filly heading in the right direction. Beat inferior opposition in good style first-up with a slick victory over 1000m at Queanbeyan. Deserves her chance at this level and will prove hard to run down with Keating's 3kg claim. GAMBLER (4) returned excellent closing splits from near last on the turn when resumed with a narrow second over 1100m at Hawkesbury. Drops in trip from the better draw and will prove hard to hold out. DIVA LAS VEGAS (5) returns from a lengthy spell. Started ($1.55 fav) on debut when a sharp winner over 900m at Newcastle on the Heavy 8 surface. Impressed in both trials and will need a good ride from the gate. LULL (6) resumes, and is now in the Maher stable. Impressed in her first campaign with a Maiden win over this track and trip. Fitted with the one trial and the tongue-tie goes on.
